summary: So I decided to make another mod today, since I haven\'t created a mod yet for ages now. This mod is the Whiterun Skill Room!
descriptionHtml:
So I decided to make another mod today, since I haven\'t created a mod yet for ages now. This mod is the Whiterun Skill Room!

The Whiterun Skill Room is located under a waterfall in Whiterun\'s Wind District.

Inside of the Skill Room you will find an Enchanting section, with a chest with four random items with enchantments!

An Alchemy section, with another chest filled to the brim with ingredients!

Smithing station, where all the smithing tools can be used. (No chest yet, sorry.)

There will also be much much more to come!
author: Windwhistle
